  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Salad Bowl Maker (Service/ Kitchen crew)",
  "description": "<h3><strong>About the Role</strong></h3><p>At <strong>Urban Mix</strong>, our Salad Bowl Makers (Urban Mixers) are at the heart of what we do. You’ll be preparing fresh, made-to-order bowls, supporting the kitchen, and delivering friendly service even during busy hours.</p><p>If you enjoy working with food, people, and a fast-paced environment, we’d love to meet you. <br />Both Full and Part-time positions are available.</p><h3><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></h3><h3><strong>As a Salad Bowl Maker (Service)</strong></h3><ul><li>Prepare salad bowls based on customer selections</li><li>Serve customers in a friendly, approachable manner</li><li>Handle queues efficiently during peak hours</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and good personal hygiene at all times</li><li>Support basic food preparation when needed</li></ul><h3><strong>As Kitchen Crew</strong></h3><ul><li>Assist with food preparation and cooking</li><li>Follow recipes, portioning, and food safety standards</li><li>Keep the kitchen clean, organised, and well-stocked</li><li>Work closely with the team to ensure smooth service</li></ul><h3><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></h3><ul><li>Friendly and service-oriented</li><li>Quick, efficient, and able to handle long queues</li><li>Comfortable working in a fast-paced environment</li><li>Strong sense of cleanliness and personal hygiene</li><li>Team player with a positive attitude</li><li><strong>Food Safety and Hygiene certification is a plus</strong></li></ul><p>✨ <strong>Good attitude matters more than experience</strong></p><p>Training will be provided for the right candidate.</p><h3><strong>Why Join Urban Mix</strong></h3><ul><li>Supportive and friendly team culture</li><li>Hands-on training provided</li><li>Opportunity to grow with a growing brand</li><li>A workplace that values teamwork, respect, and pride in what we serve<br /></li></ul>",
